    scope: global
    category: architecture
    content: 'UI DSL pattern: Import DSL functions with `local dsl =
      require("ui.ui_syntax_sugar")` and use `dsl.spawn(element, config)` to
      instantiate UI panels. Elements are composed using container functions
      like `dsl.vstack()`, `dsl.hstack()`, and `dsl.zstack()` that accept tables
      of child elements. Each element returns a Defold node that can be further
      manipulated.'
